---
---

<section class="privacy section" id="privacy">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="copy">
        <span class="kicker">Privacy by default</span>
        <h2>What's recorded on your phone stays on your phone.</h2>
        <p>
          Dashcam.io is designed so that you never have to trust a server with
          your driving footage. Video lives in the app's private storage.
          Object detection runs on-device with MediaPipe. AI trip summaries run
          on-device with Gemma 3. The only time a clip leaves the device is
          when you explicitly tap <strong>Share</strong>, or when a crash
          auto-upload fires on a premium plan — and even then, uploads go
          through a per-user signed URL with a 7-day expiry.
        </p>
        <ul class="checks">
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m5 12 5 5L20 7"/></svg>
            Video never leaves the device by default
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m5 12 5 5L20 7"/></svg>
            Object detection runs 100% offline
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m5 12 5 5L20 7"/></svg>
            AI summaries run on the phone, not in the cloud
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m5 12 5 5L20 7"/></svg>
            No tracking, no third-party analytics on the web
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .privacy {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .card {
    background: linear-gradient(165deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fcfc 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 64px 56px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px;
    right: -100px;
    width: 320px;
    height: 320px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 199, 190, 0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .copy {
    max-width: 680px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  p strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .checks {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px 24px;
  }

  .checks li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .checks svg {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding: 4px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .card {
      padding: 40px 28px;
    }
  }
</style>
